name: Pink Elephant featuring Drunky McSkunky
description:
Here it is!!! Amanda Visell’s first vinyl toy. Edition of 600 in full color window box. Approx 7” tall with Drunky’s magnetic butt perched on top.

	Translating an artists two dimensional work into a three dimensional object is always tricky. Sculpted by Amanda herself, Munky King really ran with this one creating a fantastic pieces that really does justice to her fine work.

name: Soopa Coin-Up Bros. D-I-Y
description:
Here is the brand new Soopa Coin-Up Bros. D-I-Y vinyl toy created by Erick Scarecrow and manufactured by Esc-Toy Ltd. The Soopa is 7" arcade vinyl toy and comes with Soopa stickers that can be used to design a screen, marquee, and wrapping cabinet art. Dedicated to the game heads worldwide!!!
